'''窒息式性爱'''（{{lang-en|erotic asphyxiation}}、{{lang|en|breath control play}}）是指为了获得[[性刺激|性快感]]，故意限制大脑供[[氧|氧]]的行为。该做法利用人體在[[缺氧|缺氧]]、[[窒息|窒息]]的瞬間，局部器官的高度收縮，而使自己或對方從中得到性快感和[[性高潮|性高潮]]，但常有不小心而令人死亡的事件發生。如果是[[自慰|自慰]]时进行此行为，则会被称为'''自慰性窒息'''（{{lang-en|autoerotic asphyxiation}}）。在[[美國精神醫學學會|美國精神醫學學會]]的《[[精神疾病診斷與統計手冊|精神疾病診斷與統計手冊]]》中，窒息式性爱被归于[[性偏離|性偏離]]的一种。

== 生理 ==
约翰·库拉（{{lang|en|John Curra}}）写道，“脖子两侧的[[總頸動脈|總頸動脈]]负责将含有[[氧|氧]]的血液从心脏运输到大脑中。当因吊颈而使得该血管受到挤压时，大脑会突然缺氧，[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]也开始堆积，此时会有头晕目眩的感觉并伴有愉悦感，这些会使得自慰带来的快感度升高。”<ref>{{cite book|title=The Relativity of Deviance|url=https://archive.org/details/relativityofdevi00john|author=John Curra|publisher=Sage Publications, Inc.|location=Thousand Oaks, California|year=2000|page=[https://archive.org/details/relativityofdevi00john/page/111 111]|isbn=0-7619-0778-5}}</ref>乔治·舒曼（{{lang|en|George Shuman}}）将该影响描写为“当大脑供氧不足时，它会进入到被称为[[缺氧|缺氧]]的状态，此状态下人会保持清醒，但却处在半致幻状态。该感觉与[[性高潮|性高潮]]结合，带来的快感不比[[可卡因|可卡因]]差，也非常容易上瘾。”<ref>{{cite book|title=Last Breath: A Sherry Moore Novel|url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781416534914|author=George D. Shuman|publisher=Simon & Schuster|year=2007|page=[https://archive.org/details/isbn_9781416534914/page/n89 80]|isbn=1-4165-3491-1}}</ref>

关于窒息式性爱因缺氧所带来的幻觉，E·劳埃德（{{lang|en|E L Lloyd}}）指出，这种幻觉可能与身处在高海拔地区的攀岩者感受到的幻觉类似。他还指出，飞机在高海拔处突然减压并不会带来这种幻觉，因此这一感觉可能并不是单纯因缺氧而起。在回顾了有关缺氧方面的文献后，他发现“[[神经递质|神经递质]]、[[多巴胺|多巴胺]]、[[血清素|血清素]]和{{tsl|en|Beta-endorphin|β-内啡肽}}，它们会互相影响，并导致大脑神经化学的异常。这种异常变化在所有的致幻情形中都有出现。”<ref>{{cite journal|title= Points: Hallucinations, hypoxia, and neurotransmitters|author=Dr. E L Lloyd|publisher=British Medical Journal Volume 292| date=1986-03-29|page=903}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
自慰性窒息从17世纪便有所记载，起先是用来治疗[[勃起功能障碍|勃起功能障碍]]的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sataniclust.com/04_06/pro_0406_asphyxiation.htm|title=Erotic Asphyxiation|work=Lust Magazine|year=1997|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060831011633/http://www.sataniclust.com/04_06/pro_0406_asphyxiation.htm|archivedate=2006-08-31|access-date=2018-05-06}}</ref>这种疗法很可能源自被[[绞刑|绞刑]]者，人们注意到男性受刑者出现了[[勃起|勃起]]的现象，有时能够持续到死亡之后（即[[死亡勃起|死亡勃起]]），偶尔亦会伴有[[射精|射精]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=5 Weird Things That Happen When You Die|url=https://www.menshealth.com/health/a19547721/body-effects-after-death/|website=Men's Health|accessdate=2018-05-07|date=2015-09-18|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180507153311/https://www.menshealth.com/health/a19547721/body-effects-after-death/|archivedate=2018-05-07}}</ref>

== 方式 ==
悬挂、用塑料袋闷住头部、自己{{tsl|en|strangulation|勒}}住自己（比如使用[[結紮|绳结]]）、利用气体或易挥发溶质、挤压胸腔等不同方式（或对这些方式加以结合）都能达到窒息式性愛所需要的耗氧量<ref name = Blanchard1991/>，也有的人会使用一些更为复杂的装置来达到此目的<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = O'Halloran | first1 = R. L. | last2 = Dietz | first2 = P. E. | year = 1993 | title = Autoerotic fatalities with power hydraulics | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-forensic-sciences_1993-03_38_2/page/359| journal = Journal of Forensic Sciences | volume = 38 | issue = | pages = 359–364 }}</ref>。哪怕小心谨慎地进行，窒息式性爱也很危险，已造成大量的意外身亡事故。尤瓦（{{lang|en|Uva}}）1995年称，“据估计，自慰性窒息会造成美国每年250至1000不等的死亡人数。”<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Uva | first1 = J. L. | year = 1995 | title = Review: Autoerotic asphyxiation in the United States | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-forensic-sciences_1995-07_40_4/page/574| journal = Journal of Forensic Sciences | volume = 40 | issue = 4| pages = 574–581 | pmid = 7595293 }}</ref>[[斯堪的纳维亚|斯堪的纳维亚]]<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1007/BF01543193 | last1 = Innala | first1 = S. M. | last2 = Ernulf | first2 = K. F. | year = 1989 | title = Asphyxiophilia in Scandinavia | url = | journal = Archives of Sexual Behavior | volume = 18 | issue = 3| pages = 181–189 | pmid = 2787626 }}</ref>和[[德国|德国]]<ref name = Janssen2005>{{Cite journal | last1 = Janssen | first1 = W. | last2 = Koops | first2 = E. | last3 = Anders | first3 = S. | last4 = Kuhn | first4 = S. | last5 = Püschel | first5 = K. | year = 2005 | title = Forensic aspects of 40 accidental autoerotic death in Northern Germany | doi =10.1016/j.forsciint.2004.09.093 | journal = Forensic Science International | volume = 147S | issue = | pages = S61–S64 | pmid=15694733}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Koops | first1 = E. | last2 = Janssen | first2 = W. | last3 = Anders | first3 = S. | last4 = Püschel | first4 = K. | year = 2005 | title = Unusual phenomenology of autoerotic fatalities | doi = 10.1016/j.forsciint.2004.09.095 | journal = Forensic Science International | volume = 147S | issue = | pages = S65–S67 | pmid=15694734}}</ref>亦有类似报告。自慰性窒息常常被误判为自杀，也是青少年的常见死亡原因之一。<ref>{{cite web | last = Downs | first = Martin | title = The Highest Price For Pleasure: A Deadly Turn-On | publisher = WebMD | date = 2005-01-01 | url = http://www.medicinenet.com/script/main/art.asp?articlekey=51776 | accessdate = 2011-10-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111228035100/http://www.medicinenet.com/script/main/art.asp?articlekey=51776 | archivedate = 2011-12-28 }}</ref>

== 意外死亡 ==
{{See also2|{{tsl|en|Autoerotic fatality|自慰死亡}}}}

在窒息式性爱中，部分缺氧的状况常常会导致人失去意识，从而失去对悬挂绳索的控制，并进一步导致缺氧，最终死亡。尽管有窒息癖的人们经常会和别人一起进行性爱活动，但对方通常因过于投入而忽略了被窒息者可能处在的危险境地。<ref>[http://www.soc.ucsb.edu/sexinfo/article/autoerotic-asphyxiophilia Autoerotic Asphyxiophilia] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090515161226/http://www.soc.ucsb.edu/sexinfo/article/autoerotic-asphyxiophilia |date=2009-05-15 }} on 'Sexinfo' website, University of Santa Barbara, Ca.</ref>

在部分死亡案例中，窒息癖死者的尸体被发现时全裸或手握性器，身旁有情色材料、性玩具，有死前高潮过的迹象。<ref name = Janssen2005/>这些意外死亡现场常常会有死者生前曾进行其他[[性偏離|性偏離]]活动的迹象，<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1097/00000433-199103000-00012 | last1 = Bogliolo | first1 = L. R. | last2 = Taff | first2 = M. L. | last3 = Stephens | first3 = P. J. | last4 = Money | first4 = J. | year = 1991 | title = A case of autoerotic asphyxia associated with multiplex paraphilia | url = | journal = American Journal of Forensic Medicine and Pathology | volume = 12 | issue = 1| pages = 64–73 | pmid = 2063821 }}</ref>如[[異裝|女装癖]]、受虐癖。<ref name = Blanchard1991>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1192/bjp.159.3.371 | last1 = Blanchard | first1 = R. | last2 = Hucker | first2 = S. J. | year = 1991 | title = Age, transvestism, bondage, and concurrent paraphilic activities in 117 fatal cases of autoerotic asphyxia | url = | journal = British Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 159 | issue = 3| pages = 371–377 | pmid = 1958948 }}</ref>如果死者是在家中居住的青少年，家属通常会“打扫”现场，将这些性偏离的证据清理掉，结果破坏了现场，导致死者看上去像是故意自杀而非意外身亡。<ref>Downs, Martin. [http://www.medicinenet.com/script/main/art.asp?articlekey=51776 The Highest Price for Pleasure] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527022103/http://www.medicinenet.com/script/main/art.asp?articlekey=51776 |date=2016-05-27 }}, featured by WebMD</ref>

窒息式性爱导致的死者多为男性；在1974年至1987年、加拿大[[安大略省|安大略省]]和[[艾伯塔省|艾伯塔省]]所有因窒息式性爱身亡的117名死者中，只有一名是女性。<ref name = Blanchard1991/>窒息式性爱导致的意外死亡主要发生在25岁前后，<ref name = Blanchard1991/><ref name = Burgess1983>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1111/j.1939-0025.1983.tb03361.x | last1 = Burgess | first1 = A. W. | last2 = Hazelwood | first2 = R. R. | year = 1983 | title = Autoerotic deaths and social network response | url = | journal = {{tsl|en|American Journal of Orthopsychiatry||American Journal of Orthopsychiatry}} | volume = 53 | issue = 1| pages = 166–170 | pmid = 6829721 }}</ref>但也存在青少年<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1007/BF01564363 | last1 = Shankel | first1 = L. W. | last2 = Carr | first2 = A. C. | year = 1956 | title = Transvestism and hanging episodes in a male adolescent | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_psychiatric-quarterly_1956-07_30_3/page/478| journal = Psychiatric Quarterly | volume = 30 | issue = 3| pages = 478–493 | pmid = 13359556 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1097/00004583-198805000-00017 | last1 = Sheehan | first1 = W. | last2 = Garfinkel | first2 = B. D. | year = 1987 | title = Adolescent autoerotic deaths | url = | journal = Journal of the American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry | volume = 27 | issue = 3| pages = 367–370 | pmid = 3379021 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1192/bjp.121.4.437 | last1 = Edmondson | first1 = J. S. | year = 1972 | title = A case of sexual asphyxis without fatal termination | url = | journal = British Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 121 | issue = 563| pages = 437–438 | pmid = 5077101 }}</ref>和70岁男性的死亡案例。<ref name = "Janssen2005" /><ref name = "Burgess1983" />

因为律师和保险公司的缘故，这些窒息式性爱的案例引起了临床医生的注意——有的保险可以给意外身亡赔付，但自杀是不行的。<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Cooper | first1 = A. J. | year = 1995 | title = "Auto-erotic asphyxial death: Analysis of nineteen fatalities in Alberta": Comment | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_canadian-journal-of-psychiatry_1995-08_40_6/page/363| journal = Canadian Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 40 | issue = | pages = 363–364 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Cooper | first1 = A. J. | year = 1996 | title = Auto-erotic asphyxiation: Three case reports | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-sex-and-marital-therapy_spring-1996_22_1/page/47| journal = Journal of Sex and Marital Therapy | volume = 22 | issue = 1| pages = 47–53 | pmid = 8699497 | doi = 10.1080/00926239608405305 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Garza-Leal | first1 = J. A. | last2 = Landrom | first2 = F. J. | year = 1991 | title = Autoerotic death initially misinterpreted as suicide and a review of the literature | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-forensic-sciences_1991-11_36_6/page/1753| journal = Journal of Forensic Sciences | volume = 36 | issue = 6| pages = 1753–1759 | pmid = 1770343 }}</ref>

